#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.35"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.35:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.35:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga"
msgstr "4. Deities"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.35:0.3"
msgid "35. Dutiyasovacassatāsutta"
msgstr "35. Easy to Admonish (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.30"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.35:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā "
"abhikkantavaṇṇā … pe …"
msgstr "“Mendicants, tonight a deity … said to me:"

msgctxt "an7.35:1.2"
msgid "‘sattime, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, these seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an7.35:1.3"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.35:1.4"
msgid ""
"Satthugāravatā, dhammagāravatā, saṅghagāravatā, sikkhāgāravatā, "
"samādhigāravatā, sovacassatā, kalyāṇamittatā."
msgstr ""
"Respect for the Teacher, for the teaching, for the Saṅgha, for the training, "
"for immersion; being easy to admonish, and good friendship."

msgctxt "an7.35:1.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhante, satta dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī’ti."
msgstr "These seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.’"

msgctxt "an7.35:1.6"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, sā devatā."
msgstr "That is what that deity said."

msgctxt "an7.35:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Then he bowed and respectfully circled me, keeping me on his right side, "
"before vanishing right there.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.35:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā sāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Sāriputta said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an7.35:2.2"
msgid ""
"“imassa kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena "
"atthaṃ ājānāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, this is how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief "
"statement."

msgctxt "an7.35:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhante, bhikkhu attanā ca satthugāravo hoti, satthugāravatāya ca "
"vaṇṇavādī."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant personally respects the Teacher and praises such "
"respect."

msgctxt "an7.35:2.4"
msgid "Ye caññe bhikkhū na satthugāravā te ca satthugāravatāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""
"And they encourage other mendicants who lack such respect to respect the "
"Teacher."

msgctxt "an7.35:2.5"
msgid ""
"Ye caññe bhikkhū satthugāravā tesañca vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena."
msgstr ""
"And they praise other mendicants who respect the Teacher at the right time, "
"truthfully and substantively."

msgctxt "an7.35:2.6"
msgid "Attanā ca dhammagāravo hoti … pe …"
msgstr "They personally respect the teaching …"

msgctxt "an7.35:2.7"
msgid "saṅghagāravo hoti …"
msgstr "They personally respect the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "an7.35:2.8"
msgid "sikkhāgāravo hoti …"
msgstr "They personally respect the training …"

msgctxt "an7.35:2.9"
msgid "samādhigāravo hoti …"
msgstr "They personally respect immersion …"

msgctxt "an7.35:2.10"
msgid "suvaco hoti …"
msgstr "They are personally easy to admonish …"

msgctxt "an7.35:2.11"
msgid "kalyāṇamitto hoti, kalyāṇamittatāya ca vaṇṇavādī."
msgstr "They personally have good friends, and praise such friendship."

msgctxt "an7.35:2.12"
msgid "Ye caññe bhikkhū na kalyāṇamittā te ca kalyāṇamittatāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""
"And they encourage other mendicants who lack good friends to develop good "
"friendship."

msgctxt "an7.35:2.13"
msgid ""
"Ye caññe bhikkhū kalyāṇamittā tesañca vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālenāti."
msgstr ""
"And they praise other mendicants who have good friends at the right time, "
"truthfully and substantively."

msgctxt "an7.35:2.14"
msgid ""
"Imassa kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena "
"atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief "
"statement.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.31"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.35:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

msgctxt "an7.35:3.2"
msgid ""
"Sādhu kho tvaṃ, sāriputta, imassa mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ "
"vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsi."
msgstr ""
"It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of what I’ve said in "
"brief like this."

msgctxt "an7.35:3.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, sāriputta, bhikkhu attanā ca satthugāravo hoti, satthugāravatāya ca "
"vaṇṇavādī."
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant personally respects the Teacher …"

msgctxt "an7.35:3.4"
msgid "Ye caññe bhikkhū na satthugāravā te ca satthugāravatāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""
"And they encourage other mendicants who lack such respect to respect the "
"Teacher."

msgctxt "an7.35:3.5"
msgid ""
"Ye caññe bhikkhū satthugāravā tesañca vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena."
msgstr ""
"And they praise other mendicants who respect the Teacher at the right time, "
"truthfully and substantively."

msgctxt "an7.35:3.6"
msgid "Attanā ca dhammagāravo hoti … pe …"
msgstr "They personally respect the teaching …"

msgctxt "an7.35:3.7"
msgid "saṅghagāravo hoti …"
msgstr "They personally respect the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "an7.35:3.8"
msgid "sikkhāgāravo hoti …"
msgstr "They personally respect the training …"

msgctxt "an7.35:3.9"
msgid "samādhigāravo hoti …"
msgstr "They personally respect immersion …"

msgctxt "an7.35:3.10"
msgid "suvaco hoti …"
msgstr "They are personally easy to admonish …"

msgctxt "an7.35:3.11"
msgid "kalyāṇamitto hoti, kalyāṇamittatāya ca vaṇṇavādī."
msgstr "They personally have good friends, and praise such friendship."

msgctxt "an7.35:3.12"
msgid "Ye caññe bhikkhū na kalyāṇamittā te ca kalyāṇamittatāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""
"And they encourage other mendicants who lack good friends to develop good "
"friendship."

msgctxt "an7.35:3.13"
msgid ""
"Ye caññe bhikkhū kalyāṇamittā tesañca vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālenāti."
msgstr ""
"And they praise other mendicants who have good friends at the right time, "
"truthfully and substantively."

msgctxt "an7.35:3.14"
msgid ""
"Imassa kho, sāriputta, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho "
"daṭṭhabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what I said in brief.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.35:3.15"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
